The Glenn Beck Program




Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



   
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/19/13Thursday, December 19, 2013 10:30 AM



Glenn is upset about how Duck Dynasty's Phil Robertson is being attacked 
                                                     for expressing his beliefs 
       and how it's important to stand up for our values.

  Also, Glenn's close friend Pastor Ken Hutcherson passed away and Glenn reflects.

  Plus, the guys count down their favorite sound clips of the year from mainstream media.
